<%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main class="container"
        style="max-width: 800px; margin: 4rem auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; color: #334155; line-height: 1.8;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Refund Policy</h1>
        <p>Last updated: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString() %>
        </p>

        <div
            style="background: #fffbfa; border: 1px solid #fed7aa; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; margin: 2.5rem 0;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #c2410c; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 1rem;">No Refunds After Booking
            </h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #9a3412; font-weight: 500;">
                We do not allow refunds after a successful booking has been made.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Once payment is processed and your 1:1 session is confirmed on the host's
                calendar, the platform reserves the time exclusively for you. Therefore, cancellations or no-shows are
                strictly non-refundable.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #0f172a; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Host Cancellations</h2>
        <p>In the rare event that a host cancels an upcoming session and cannot offer a rescheduled time, you will be
            issued a full refund directly to your original payment method. Host no-shows are strictly monitored.</p>

        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: #0f172a; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Contact & Support</h2>
        <p>If you encounter an emergency or technical failure on our platform that prevented you from joining your
            session, please reach out to us:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@gurubrahma.online"
                style="color: #4f46e5;">support@gurubrahma.online</a></p>
        <p><strong>Address:</strong><br>
            T-Hub Foundation,<br>
            1/C, 83/1, Raidurgam panmaktha,<br>
            Hyderabad Knowledge City, SERILINGAMPALLY,<br>
            Hyderabad, Telangana 500081, India
        </p>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>